Title: spring-projects/spring-ai: An Application Framework for AI Engineering
URL: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai
Content: We read every piece of feedback, and take your input very seriously. ## Use saved searches to filter your results more quickly. # spring-projects/spring-ai. | spring-ai-bom | | spring-ai-bom |  |  |. | spring-ai-commons | | spring-ai-commons |  |  |. | spring-ai-docs | | spring-ai-docs |  |  |. | spring-ai-integration-tests | | spring-ai-integration-tests |  |  |. | spring-ai-model | | spring-ai-model |  |  |. | spring-ai-rag | | spring-ai-rag |  |  |. | spring-ai-retry | | spring-ai-retry |  |  |. | spring-ai-spring-boot-docker-compose | | spring-ai-spring-boot-docker-compose |  |  |. | spring-ai-spring-boot-testcontainers | | spring-ai-spring-boot-testcontainers |  |  |. | spring-ai-test | | spring-ai-test |  |  |. The Spring AI project provides a Spring-friendly API and abstractions for developing AI applications. At its core, Spring AI addresses the fundamental challenge of AI integration: connecting your enterprise **Data** and **APIs** with the **AI Models**. If you want to try out the latest and greatest, Spring AI can be built and published to your local Maven repository:.

