Title: The Fable 5 Backlash Is Getting Serious - YouTube
URL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LzBF70aI6k
Content: The Fable 5 Backlash Is Getting Serious
AI Revolution
552000 subscribers
225 likes
2725 views
11 Jun 2026
Claude Fable 5 is already facing huge backlash, and the reason is bigger than simple safety filters. Users say Anthropic’s newest Claude model is refusing harmless prompts, triggering false alarms, and in some cases limiting advanced AI-related work in ways that were not clearly visible at first. Fable 5 may still be one of the most powerful public AI models ever released, but the controversy is now about trust: when Claude gives you an answer, are you getting the real Fable 5, a downgraded Opus fallback, or a weakened version shaped behind the scenes?

